        <h1>AI Courses</h1>
        
            <p>Artificial Intelligence (AI) refers to the simulation of human intelligence in machines that are programmed to think, learn, and problem-solve like humans.</p>
            <p>It involves creating algorithms and models that enable computers to perform tasks such as decision-making, pattern recognition, language understanding, and even visual perception.</p>
            <p>AI can be classified into narrow AI (designed for specific tasks) and general AI (which would exhibit human-like cognitive abilities across a wide range of activities).</p>
            <p>AI is used in applications like speech recognition, autonomous driving, healthcare, and more.</p>
        <h2>Application of AI</h2>
                <ul>
