                <li>Security:</li>
                    <p>AI is used for facial recognition by identifying people from images or videos. This technology is used for security purposes, such as identifying criminals or unauthorized individuals.</p>
                <li>Marketing:</li>
                    <p>I is used for targeted advertising by showing ads to people who are most likely to be interested in the product or service being advertised. For example, social media companies use AI to target ads to users based on their interests and demographics.</p>
                <li>Education:</li>
